prototype.arguments</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/caller\"><code>Function.prototype.caller</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/displayName\"><code>Function.prototype.displayName</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/length\"><code>Function.prototype.length</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/name\"><code>Function.prototype.name</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/prototype\"><code>Function.prototype.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Metody</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/apply\"><code>Function.prototype.apply()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/bind\"><code>Function.prototype.bind()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/call\"><code>Function.prototype.call()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/toString\"><code>Function.prototype.toString()</code></a></li></ol></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Własności</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Metody</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Objekt<strong> <code>ArrayBuffer</code></strong> reprezentuje buffer z surowymi danymi binarnymi o niezmiennej długości. Nie możesz bezpośrednio wpływać na zawartość obiektu <code><strong>ArrayBuffer</strong></code>, możesz natomiast stworzyć jeden z obiektów<code> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypedArray\">typedArray</a></code> lub obiekt <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/DataView\"><code>DataView</code></a> reprezentujący buffer w specjalnym formacie i używać tego obiektu do odczytu oraz zapisu treści buffera.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"składnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">new ArrayBuffer(length)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parametry","title":"Parametry","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"długość\">długość<code>(length)</code></dt>\n <dd>Rozmiar, w bajtach, tworzony z bufferu tablicy (array buffer).</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"wartość_zwrócona","title":"Wartość zwrócona","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Nowy obiekt <code>ArrayBuffer</code> o określonym rozmiarze. Jego wartości początkowe wynoszą 0.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"wyjątki","title":"Wyjątki","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/RangeError\"><code>RangeError</code></a> pojawi się, jeśli długość (<code>length</code>) jest większa niż <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number/MAX_SAFE_INTEGER\"><code>Number.MAX_SAFE_INTEGER</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> (&gt;= 2 ** 53) lub ujemna.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"opis","title":"Opis","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Konstruktor <code>ArrayBuffer</code> tworzy nowy <code>ArrayBuffer </code>z podanej długości (<code>length</code>) w bajtach.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"otrzymywanie_bufferu_tablicy_z_istniejących_danych","title":"Otrzymywanie bufferu tablicy z istniejących danych","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Base64#appendix.3a_decode_a_base64_string_to_uint8array_or_arraybuffer\">ze stringa Base64</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader#readasarraybuffer()\">z lokalnego pliku</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"właściwości","title":"Właściwości","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"arraybuffer.length\"><code>ArrayBuffer.length</code></dt>\n <dd>Właściwość długości konstruktura <code>ArrayBuffer</code>, której wartość wynosi 1.</dd>\n <dt id=\"get_arraybufferspecies_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/@@species\"><code>get ArrayBuffer[@@species]</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Funkcja konstruktora jest używana do tworzenia dostarczanych obiektów.</dd>\n <dt id=\"arraybuffer.prototype_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Pozwala dodać właściwości do wszystkich obiektów <code>ArrayBuffer</code>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"metody","title":"Metody","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"arraybuffer.isviewarg_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/isView\"><code>ArrayBuffer.isView(arg)</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Zwraca <code>true</code>, jeśli <code>arg</code> jest jednym z widoków <code>ArrayBuffer</code>, jak obiekty <code>typedArray</code> lub <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/DataView\"><code>DataView</code></a>. W innych przypadkach zwraca <code>false</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"arraybuffer.transferoldbuffer_newbytelength\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>ArrayBuffer.transfer(oldBuffer [, newByteLength])</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>\n <div class=\"line\" id=\"file-arraybuffer-transfer-lc6\">Zwraca nowy <code>ArrayBuffer</code>, którego zawartości są pobrane z danych <code>oldBuffer</code>. Następnie zostaje skrócony lub przedłużony od 0 przez <code>newByteLength</code>.</div>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"instancje_arraybuffer","title":"<code>Instancje ArrayBuffer</code>","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Wszystkie instancje <code>ArrayBuffer </code>dziedziczą z <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>","titleAsText":"Instancje ArrayBuffer"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"właściwości_2","title":"Właściwości","isH3":true,"content":"<p>{{page('en-US/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/prototype','Properties')}}</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"metody_2","title":"Metody","isH3":true,"content":"<p>{{page('en-US/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/prototype','Methods')}}</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"arraybuffer.slice_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/slice\"><code>ArrayBuffer.slice()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Posiada tę samą funkcjonalność, jak <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer/slice\"><code>ArrayBuffer.prototype.slice()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przykłady","title":"Przykłady","isH3":false,"content":"<p>W niniejszym przykładzie tworzymy 8-bajtowy buffer z widokiem <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Int32Array\"><code>Int32Array</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> odnoszącym się do buffera:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> buffer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ArrayBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> view   <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Int32Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>buffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacje","title":"Specyfikacje","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specyfikacja</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Komentarz</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.khronos.org/registry/typedarray/specs/latest/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'Typed Array Specification' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">Typed Array Specification</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsolete</span></td>\n   <td>Zastępiony przez ECMAScript 6.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-arraybuffer-constructor\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of 'ArrayBuffer' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Definicja początkowa w standardzie ECMA. Zgłasza, że wymagany jest <code>new</code>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-arraybuffer-constructor\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of 'ArrayBuffer' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"kompatybilność_z_przeglądarkami","title":"Kompatybilność z przeglądarkami","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">We're converting our compatibility data into a machine-readable JSON format</a></strong>.\n            This compatibility table still uses the old format,\n            because we haven't yet converted the data it contains.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Find out how you can help! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Pulpit</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Cecha</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Wsparcie podstawowe</td>\n   <td>7.0</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/4\" title=\"Released on 2011-03-22.\">4.0</a> (2)</td>\n   <td>10</td>\n   <td>11.6</td>\n   <td>5.1</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>ArrayBuffer()</code> bez odsyłacza <code>new</code></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/44\" title=\"Released on 2016-01-26.\">44</a> (44)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>ArrayBuffer.slice()</code> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span><br>\n    <span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/53\" title=\"Released on 2017-04-18.\">53</a> (53)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Cecha</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Wsparcie podstawowe</td>\n   <td>4.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>4.0 (2)</td>\n   <td>10</td>\n   <td>11.6</td>\n   <td>4.2</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>ArrayBuffer()</code> bez odsyłacza <code>new</code></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>44.0 (44)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>ArrayBuffer.slice()</code> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span><br>\n    <span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span> 53.0 (53)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">No&nbsp;support</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zapis_kompatybilny","title":"Zapis kompatybilny","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Od ECMAScript 2015 kontruktory <code>ArrayBuffer</code> muszą być tworzone poprzez operator <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/new\"><code>new</code></a>. Wywoływanie kontruktora ArrayBuffer jako funkcji bez <code>new</code> zaskutkuje od teraz pojawieniem się <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>TypeError</code></a>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js example-bad notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> dv <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">ArrayBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// TypeError: calling a builtin ArrayBuffer constructor</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/